# Code conventions

- Minimize scope; match existing file patterns
- Import Prisma from `@/generated/prisma/client`; use `prisma` from `@/lib/db`
- Card lookups: local Postgres only — never `fetch` Scryfall in API routes used by editor/search
- Sync scripts live in `scripts/sync/`; run via npm scripts, not from API routes in MVP
- Analysis logic: pure functions, testable; heavy work uses pre-computed `Card` roles/themes
- English strings for user-facing copy and DB enum values
